title: Wire make gen-agents-check into CI (caught broken generator in docs audit)
---
The builtin-agent prompt generator (scripts/gen_agent_builtins.sh) was broken (emitted mk missing the cwd field -> non-compiling regen) and 7 archetype .md files had drifted from code. This went undetected because make gen-agents-check is not wired into CI (.github/workflows/ci.yml has no reference). Add a gen-agents-check step to CI so generator/prompt drift fails the build going forward. Found in docs-audit (lane I, F13) + recommended in P7 completion report.